==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Imperate
<hw>Im"pe*rate</hw> <pr>(⟦icr⟧m"p⟦esl⟧*r⟦asl⟧t)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[L. <ets>imperatus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>imperare</ets> to
command.]</ety> <def>Done by express direction; not involuntary;
commanded.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Those <qex>imperate</qex> acts, wherein we see the empire of the
soul.</q> <rj><qau>Sir M. Hale.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Imperatival</ent>⟦br⟧
